  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK175">
<l>aḵki yakaṉṟa vaṟiveṉṉām yārmāṭṭum</l>
<l>veḵki veṟiya ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is the advantage of extensive and accurate knowledge if a man through covetousness act senselessly towards all ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
